# Database Architecture

Example Prisma schema:

```prisma
model User {

    id Int
        @id
        @default(autoincrement())

    email String
        @unique

    role String

    posts Post[]
}
```

---

```prisma
model Post {

    id Int
        @id
        @default(autoincrement())

    title String

    content String

    authorId Int

    author User
        @relation(
            fields:[authorId],
            references:[id]
        )
}
