# Service Layer

Large applications add:

```text
services/
```

---

Example:

```text
services/

    publishing.ts
    notifications.ts
    analytics.ts
```

---

# Example

```tsx
export async function publishPost(
    id: number
) {

    await db.post.update({

        where: { id },

        data: {
            published: true,
        },

    });

    revalidateTag(
        "posts"
    );

}
```

