# Cache Architecture

Every repository decides:

```text
Should cache?
How long?
What tags?
```

---

Example:

```tsx
export async function getUsers() {

    "use cache";

    cacheLife("hours");

    cacheTag(
        "users"
    );

    return db.user.findMany();

}
```

