# Parallel Data Fetching

Bad:

```tsx
const users =
    await getUsers();

const posts =
    await getPosts();

const comments =
    await getComments();
```

---

Good:

```tsx
const [

    users,

    posts,

    comments,

] = await Promise.all([

    getUsers(),

    getPosts(),

    getComments(),

]);
```

